# Resend API key for the Coming Soon email capture (/api/subscribe)
# Dedicated full_access key, separate from the transactional-sending key
# used by Supabase SMTP — least-privilege, independently revocable.
# Requires a Contact Property named "source" to exist in Resend first
# (Dashboard → Contacts → Properties, or via resend.contactProperties.create).
RESEND_API_KEY=
